[I] KDE Frameworks solution for spell checking

[T] Sonnet is a plugin-based spell checking library for Qt-based applications.
[T] It supports several different plugins, including HSpell, Enchant, ASpell
[T] and HUNSPELL.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/frameworks/sonnet

